@apiHost = http://localhost:5108
@btsApiHost = http://localhost:5118
@accessToken = paste-token-here
@cartId = 1
@mainLineId = paste-main-line-id-here

# 使用前請先啟動 AppleBTS compose:
# docker compose -f compose/applebts.compose.yaml up --build
#
# 若要驗證 TimeProvider 的 BTS 時間窗:
# 1. BTS 期間內
#    env Time__Mode=Shifted Time__ExpectedStartupLocal='2026-04-04T18:35:00' Time__TimeZoneId=Asia/Taipei docker compose -f compose/applebts.compose.yaml up --build
# 2. BTS 期間外
#    env Time__Mode=Shifted Time__ExpectedStartupLocal='2026-01-01T18:35:00' Time__TimeZoneId=Asia/Taipei docker compose -f compose/applebts.compose.yaml up --build
#
# 建議順序:
# authorize -> token -> catalog -> qualification/verify -> create cart -> add main -> add gift -> estimate

### OAuth authorize (從 Location header 取出 code)
POST {{apiHost}}/api/login/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=local-user&password=ignored&client_id=local-http&redirect_uri=https://localhost/callback&state=applebts

### OAuth token exchange
POST {{apiHost}}/api/login/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

code=paste-oauth-code-here

### 讀取 BTS 商品目錄
GET {{btsApiHost}}/bts-api/catalog

### 送出教育資格驗證
POST {{btsApiHost}}/bts-api/qualification/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@campus.edu.tw"
}

### 建立購物車
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 加入主商品
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/{{cartId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "macbook-air",
  "qty": 1
}

### 加入綁定主商品的贈品
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/{{cartId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "airpods-4",
  "qty": 1,
  "parentLineId": "{{mainLineId}}"
}

### 試算 BTS 折扣
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/{{cartId}}/estimate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
